Package: appr
Type: Package
Title: Application framework for R
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Author: Stuart R. Jefferys <srjefferys@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Stuart R. Jefferys <srjefferys@gmail.com>
Description: A framework for building pluggable command line R applications
    based on descriptor files. Automatically generates a command line interface
    that supports commands from installed packages by configuring them in a
    descriptor file. Supports options at the application and command level,
    including configuration files.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
